            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "If this would be implemented I would strongly suggest to add a note to the `'exrc'` docs: most people probably want to set `'exrc'` on the last line of their init.lua to not overwrite values there. (which would feel a bit weird to me?).\n\nAlso, I wouldn't reload exrc files. See https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/34079 (although that was a bug, but in general users do not expect their config to be loaded multiple times)",
