        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "\n\nI don't quite follow the example with lspconfig, that seems a bit in the weeds, where the user has to micromanage stuff. But if we can document how to control or force exrc to do something, e.g. via `require('nvim.exrc').foo()`, then that is probably the right direction.\n\nCan someone propose a doc update :) ",
